'''''Challenge'' 73''' was a roleplaying magazine from June of [[1993]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including an adventure for ''[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]''. The article was called "[[New Character Templates: A Supplement to Star Wars' Mos Eisley Galaxy Guide]]" and was written by [[Martin Wixted]].

